node.text: Omg I would love to try a Michelin star ramen 🤩

𝐌𝐢𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐥𝐢𝐧 𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐫 𝐑𝐚𝐦𝐞𝐧 at home!⁣⁣
⁣⁣
𝐓𝐬𝐮𝐭𝐚 is the World's 𝐅𝐢𝐫𝐬𝐭 Ramen Restaurant to receive a 𝐌𝐢𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐥𝐢𝐧 𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐫.⁣
⁣⁣
Glad to find out they do 𝐈𝐬𝐥𝐚𝐧𝐝𝐰𝐢𝐝𝐞 deliveries now with 𝐟𝐫𝐞𝐞 deliveries for orders above $60.⁣⁣
⁣⁣
They are also currently running a 𝟏 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝟏 promotion for their ramen dishes! Get 𝟐 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐩𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝟏 🥰⁣⁣
⁣
